SUBSCRIBE! I promise, it's fun :1 http://bit.ly/SubscribeKHS
Here's a cool mashup I did of Payphone and Call Me Maybe with three very talented and AWESOME musicians that haven't been on the channel before: Jessica Jarrell, James Alan and Jake Broido. And yes, that's a real payphone in the song and video!!
